20 other procedures for keeping information current and accurate and for recording the citizenship statuses for
21 registered electors;
22 (b) proper maintenance and use of active and inactive lists;
23 (c) proper maintenance and use of lists for legally registered electors and provisionally registered
24 electors;
25 (d) technical security of the statewide voter registration system;
26 (e) information security with respect to keeping from general public distribution driver's license
27 numbers, whole or partial social security numbers, and address information protected from general disclosure
28 pursuant to 13-2-115; and
